name: ARMANI EAU DE NUIT OUD
description: Powerful, but never harsh, the structure of Eau de Nuit Oud is incisive and intense. The scent delivers light fluid notes which, like a precious lightweight fabric, delicately sit on the skin. Oud wood is fragrance couture, absolutely Armani.
ingredients: ['Oud / Agarwood', 'Rose', 'Saffron', 'Cypriol / Nagarmota', 'Guaiac Wood', 'Geranium', 'Iris / Orris', 'Tonka Bean', 'Bergamot', 'Cardamom', 'Pink Pepper']
